thread.title: Doreen
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Doreen

author: Doreen
title: Doreen
text: My dog has been treated by the Doctor's at 2 locations. We are completely happy with the loving and caring shown by the Doctors and the entire staff . Wouldn't hesitate to take any pet here. Would highly recommend this group of Veterinary Doctors.
